Title: A Geneva Convention for the Language Wars
Date: 2014-01-17 14:30
Author: Carl
Category: Programming
Tags: programming
Slug: language-wars
Status: draft


- Languages have design goals and communities.
- Trashing languages that many people do lots of productive work in probably
  says more about you than the language
- Language design is the art of the tradeoff.
- Distinguish between a feature request and a language deficiency
- Use of the word "fail" is strongly discouraged; use of it as a noun is
  strictly prohibited
